<h2 id="iteration-2">Iteration 2</h2>

<h3 id="player">Player</h3>

<p>Create a <code class="highlighter-rouge">Player</code> class with accompanying tests.  A <code class="highlighter-rouge">Player</code> is initialized with a deck, and can determine if they have lost the game.</p>

